With this plugin, users can customize the right ContextMenu to search selected text quickly. or search in sidebar panel.
Users can export or import the configuration file from local, making it convenient for management.

1. How to add custom search menu:

1. 1 Click "New";
1.2  Fill in the name you like in the name field, fill in the search address you want to search in the search address field, such as "https://bing.com/search?ensearch=1&q={{ q }}";
1.3 Click "Save" to take effect;

2. How to get search URL:

2.1 Find the search link of the target website, such as the search link of Bing is 【https://bing.com/search?ensearch=1&q=keyword】;
2.2 Replace 【keyword】 with 【{{ q }}】， you can get the menu's URL 【https://bing.com/search?ensearch=1&q={{ q }}】;

3. How to enable search panel in page?
3.1 open `Setting Dialog` in Options, enable `Search In Page`
